> 7 Days of Breakfast Essentials Box Order ships & arrives separately from meals. Something good for everyone! This assortment comes with a variety of breakfast staples at a great cost! From drinks to help you wake up in the morning, to hearty meals to keep you going all day, this box has got it all. The best part? You never have to step foot in a grocery store. Stock up on everything from yogurts, smoothies, and eggs, to granola, overnight oats, and breakfast bars, plus teas, juice, and energy drinks.

> Your order will ship separately from your HF meals and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.

